#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Elsewhere: an ASCII Life-Sim RPG
A tiny terminal farming sim inspired by Harvest Moon / Rune Factory.

Run:
    python ascii_farmstead.py

Controls:
    WASD / Arrows / Numpad  Move (eight directions on numpad)
    F                  Use selected farm/mine tool
    Q / E              Cycle tool
    1 / 2              Cycle owned seed type
    Tab                Inventory / settings
    B                  Reopen shop menu while already standing in shop
    N                  Sleep when inside the farmhouse
    Menus              Arrow keys/WASD/numpad move, Z/Enter select, X/Esc/Q cancel
    G                  Write debug report file
    H                  Help
    C                  Toggle color
    Esc twice / Ctrl+C Quit

Notes:
- The legacy entry point remains here; static data and pure helpers now live
  in small companion modules using only Python's standard library.
- It works best in Windows Terminal, PowerShell, or a normal terminal.
"""

