                "FURNITURE CATALOG",
                "",
                "Furniture bought here can be placed inside",
                "your farmhouse from the Tab menu.",
                "",
                "Available now:",
                "- Seating, tables, rugs, plants, shelves",
                "- Lamps, mirrors, wall art, dividers",
                "- Wardrobes, dresser, fireplace, pantry",
